    • Constructor Detail

      • CplexWrapper

        public CplexWrapper(TypeModel type)
             throws ilog.concert.IloException
        Return a IloCplex instance of the given type. Cplex output and warnings are redirected to a logger. To display cplex output set log level to trace.
        Parameters:
        type - Type of the instance : Integer Program (IP) or Linear Program (LP).
        Throws:
        ilog.concert.IloException - see cplex documentation.

      • CplexWrapper

        public CplexWrapper(String s,
                    String[] strings,
                    TypeModel type)
             throws ilog.concert.IloException
        This constructor is not used. Return a IloCplex instance of the given type. Cplex output and warnings are redirected to a logger. To display cplex output set log level to trace.
        Parameters:
        s - see cplex documentation
        strings - see cplex documentation
        type - Type of the instance : Integer Program (IP) or Linear Program (LP).
        Throws:
        ilog.concert.IloException - see cplex documentation.

    • Method Detail

      • var

        public ilog.concert.IloNumVar var(int lb,
                                  int ub)
        Return an IloNumVar that encapsulate a IloIntVar or a IloNumVar accordingly to the model type of the calling cplex instance. If the instance is a IP it will return an IloIntVar. If the instance is a LP it will return an IloNumVar.
        Parameters:
        lb - lower bound
        ub - upper bound
        Returns:
        IloNumVar encapsulation of IloIntVar or IloNumVar
